   version stable 2.5 2.4 2.3pre2 2.3pre1 2.2 2.1pre37 2.1pre36 2.1pre35 
   require pcre
  optional DirectFB ''                                 --without-directfb for output using the direct frame buffer
  optional SDL      ''                                 --without-sdl      to use SDL for displaying output
  optional flex     '--enable-javascript --with-libfl' ''                 for javascript support
  optional gpm      ''                                 ''                 to use the mouse when in text mode
  optional jpeg     ''                                 ''                 for displaying jpeg graphics format
  optional libX11   --enable-graphics                  --without-x        for x11 graphics
  optional libpng   ''                                 ''                 for displaying portable network graphics
  optional openssl  --with-ssl                         --without-ssl      for HTTPS encrypted connections
  optional tiff     ''                                 ''                 for displaying TIFF images
  category network/web
 attribute client console x11
    source http://links.twibright.com/download/links-$VERSION.tar.bz2
